      <title>韩国主要反对党支持取消资本利得税计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/korea-s-main-opposition-backs-plan-to-drop-capital-gains-tax</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国主要反对党将支持政府放弃对散户投资者金融投资征收资本利得税的决定，从而放弃数月来对这一有争议举措的抗议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/korea-s-main-opposition-backs-plan-to-drop-capital-gains-tax</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 02:02:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>越南房地产大亨寻求推翻死刑判决</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/vietnam-real-estate-tycoon-seeks-to-overturn-death-sentence</link>
      <description><![CDATA[越南一家法院开始审理房地产大亨张美兰 (Truong My Lan) 的上诉，她对今年 4 月因大规模欺诈而被判处的死刑提出上诉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/vietnam-real-estate-tycoon-seeks-to-overturn-death-sentence</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 01:58:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根大通首席执行官妻子朱迪·戴蒙为卡玛拉·哈里斯敲门</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/judy-dimon-wife-of-jpmorgan-ceo-jamie-dimon-knocks-on-doors-for-kamala-harris</link>
      <description><![CDATA[著名政治捐助者、摩根大通公司高管的妻子朱迪·戴蒙周末在密歇根州拉票，支持卡玛拉·哈里斯竞选总统。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/judy-dimon-wife-of-jpmorgan-ceo-jamie-dimon-knocks-on-doors-for-kamala-harris</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 01:29:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>愤怒的民众将西班牙首相赶出洪水泛滥的城镇</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/spain-s-king-felipe-vi-prime-minister-sanchez-pelted-by-crowd-in-flooded-town</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西班牙国王和首相抵达国家悲剧现场时，一群充满敌意的人群高呼“凶手”，并向他们投掷泥巴。费利佩六世继续前行，与幸存者交谈，而佩德罗·桑切斯则钻进他的黑色轿车，抗议者跟在他身后，大声辱骂他，踢轮胎，敲打他的窗户。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/spain-s-king-felipe-vi-prime-minister-sanchez-pelted-by-crowd-in-flooded-town</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Nov 2024 23:07:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>《华尔街日报》称伊朗誓言对以色列发动“强烈而复杂的”攻击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/iran-vows-a-strong-and-complex-attack-on-israel-wsj-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[《华尔街日报》援引了解计划的伊朗和阿拉伯官员的话称，伊朗正计划使用威力更大的弹头和其他武器对以色列进行反击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/iran-vows-a-strong-and-complex-attack-on-israel-wsj-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Nov 2024 22:07:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克与特朗普的密切关系让习近平有了一位有影响力的朋友</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/musk-s-close-ties-with-trump-give-xi-a-friend-with-influence</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果美国前总统唐纳德·特朗普重新入主白宫，埃隆·马斯克成为他竞选的主要捐助者之一，对习近平来说是个好兆头。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/musk-s-close-ties-with-trump-give-xi-a-friend-with-influence</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Nov 2024 21:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员们为漫长而动荡的选举之夜做准备</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-11-03/how-traders-are-preparing-to-watch-2024-election-night-results</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着结果陆续公布，一些精神高度集中的投资者将密切关注利润率，并调整他们的赌注，直到日出为止。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-11-03/how-traders-are-preparing-to-watch-2024-election-night-results</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Nov 2024 20:00:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>民调显示哈里斯和特朗普势均力敌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/harris-trump-blitz-battlegrounds-as-final-polls-show-tight-race</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周日公布的一系列民意调查显示，副总统卡马拉·哈里斯和前总统唐纳德·特朗普在本周的总统选举中仍然势均力敌，全国选民和决定选举结果的关键摇摆州的选民支持率均以微弱差距分布。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/harris-trump-blitz-battlegrounds-as-final-polls-show-tight-race</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Nov 2024 16:49:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>内塔尼亚胡办公室被指控泄密，阻碍加沙停火</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/war-in-gaza-netanyahu-s-office-accused-of-leaks-to-thwart-cease-fire</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两个月前，当以色列和哈马斯之间似乎即将达成停火协议时，一个新的障碍出现了：以色列总理本雅明内塔尼亚胡表示，他的军队必须守住加沙和埃及边境，防止哈马斯重新武装并偷运出以色列人质。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/war-in-gaza-netanyahu-s-office-accused-of-leaks-to-thwart-cease-fire</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Nov 2024 13:42:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚总理承诺减免 105 亿美元学生债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-02/australia-plans-10-5-billion-in-student-debt-cuts-to-ease-costs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚中左翼工党政府承诺在 5 月份选举之前削减 160 亿澳元（105 亿美元）的大学和技术学院学生贷款，旨在缓解选民对生活成本上涨的不满。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-02/australia-plans-10-5-billion-in-student-debt-cuts-to-ease-costs</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 02 Nov 2024 23:45:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
